commitResults.messageBody: Added joshuatyf.png and updated the portfolio section for Joshua
This commit fixes errors mentioned in the pull request review for adding organisational related use cases.
FindCommand was previously using NameContainsKeywordPredicate. It will now use FlashcardContainsTagPredicate.
FindCommandParser was previously using NameContainsKeywordPredicate. It will now use FlashcardContainsTagPredicate.
FindCommand case was previously commented out.
DEFAULT_TAG was previously of type Tag but it is now a String and the Tag object will be initialised in the constructor of FlashcardBuilder. This is to be consistent with the Question and Answer.
